# Guardrail registry

`config/guardrails.json` lists `byAgent` paths under `guardrails/`. Coordination agents use `guardrails/platform_agent`; data governance uses `guardrails/data_governance`.

When adding an agent id to `config/agents.json`, add or reuse a matching `byAgent` entry and keep `guardrails/<domain>/rules.md` in sync.
